  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>The Crawling Chaos of Madness, the perverse fertility deity known as the Black Goat of the Woods with a Thousand Young, the All-in-One and One-in-All of limitless being and self, the trembling and radiant triakis octahedron — on the wondrous night of the Black Star's ascension, The Elder One shall descend.</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/9fc33cf6ee8818c8a293ae8897385e46.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/9fc33cf6ee8818c8a293ae8897385e46.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/9fc33cf6ee8818c8a293ae8897385e46.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Move! Move! Move!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sector is fraught with danger, but you must act. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge for food, medicine, and materials, uncover traces of the extradimensional, and eliminate monsters and the human traitors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/2bb9c2db5fe5d3d8d1bf2d809c163b90.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/2bb9c2db5fe5d3d8d1bf2d809c163b90.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/2bb9c2db5fe5d3d8d1bf2d809c163b90.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit operators to aid your cause—we'll help you find the right candidates, train their skills, and support you in completing missions and exploring the entire Sector.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll discover everything you need to upgrade your base, along with hundreds of weapon attachments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/b15f940bfece47bf7127bb5960c1437c.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/b15f940bfece47bf7127bb5960c1437c.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/b15f940bfece47bf7127bb5960c1437c.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in our meticulously designed firearm system, where you can modify weapons based on real-world designs and delve into a world of ruthless tactics and relentless firepower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/5228dc79284aa5d1c5240a1ba403a8cd.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/5228dc79284aa5d1c5240a1ba403a8cd.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/5228dc79284aa5d1c5240a1ba403a8cd.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be cautious—failure means your operators will lose all their gear!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/6e4ee243a328bbc8e97fa6afe9d43ae3.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/6e4ee243a328bbc8e97fa6afe9d43ae3.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/6e4ee243a328bbc8e97fa6afe9d43ae3.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Still, you're fortunate. Behind you stands the unwavering support of all humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Operator, welcome to the Madness.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Mission objective: Stay Alive.</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>The Crawling Chaos of Madness, the perverse fertility deity known as the Black Goat of the Woods with a Thousand Young, the All-in-One and One-in-All of limitless being and self, the trembling and radiant triakis octahedron — on the wondrous night of the Black Star's ascension, The Elder One shall descend.</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/9fc33cf6ee8818c8a293ae8897385e46.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/9fc33cf6ee8818c8a293ae8897385e46.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/9fc33cf6ee8818c8a293ae8897385e46.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Move! Move! Move!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sector is fraught with danger, but you must act. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge for food, medicine, and materials, uncover traces of the extradimensional, and eliminate monsters and the human traitors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/2bb9c2db5fe5d3d8d1bf2d809c163b90.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/2bb9c2db5fe5d3d8d1bf2d809c163b90.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/2bb9c2db5fe5d3d8d1bf2d809c163b90.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit operators to aid your cause—we'll help you find the right candidates, train their skills, and support you in completing missions and exploring the entire Sector.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll discover everything you need to upgrade your base, along with hundreds of weapon attachments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/b15f940bfece47bf7127bb5960c1437c.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/b15f940bfece47bf7127bb5960c1437c.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/b15f940bfece47bf7127bb5960c1437c.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in our meticulously designed firearm system, where you can modify weapons based on real-world designs and delve into a world of ruthless tactics and relentless firepower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/5228dc79284aa5d1c5240a1ba403a8cd.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/5228dc79284aa5d1c5240a1ba403a8cd.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/5228dc79284aa5d1c5240a1ba403a8cd.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be cautious—failure means your operators will lose all their gear!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/6e4ee243a328bbc8e97fa6afe9d43ae3.poster.avif?t=1743833518\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/6e4ee243a328bbc8e97fa6afe9d43ae3.webm?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264820/extras/6e4ee243a328bbc8e97fa6afe9d43ae3.mp4?t=1743833518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Still, you're fortunate. Behind you stands the unwavering support of all humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Operator, welcome to the Madness.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Mission objective: Stay Alive.</i></strong></p>",
